<i>noun</i>: 이야기꾼 [이야기꾼], 얘기꾼 [얘ː기꾼] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이야기꾼 [이야기꾼]</dt><br>
<dd>storyteller</dd><br>
<dd>이야기를 재미있게 잘하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who amuses people with stories.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얘기꾼 [얘ː기꾼]</dt><br>
<dd>raconteur; storyteller; anecdotist</dd><br>
<dd>이야기를 재미있게 잘하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who is skilled in telling a story interestingly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>